name: Unsweetened Candy
description:
011
_
This is an illustration image that I made based on a sketch of a drawing that was never finished in several of my sketchbook sheets, some of which I have used in my previous work and I will try to bring it back with a different atmosphere. In this work, there are many visuals that are influenced by other people's work or visual sources scattered on the internet, maybe this is a random and chaotic illustration when humans try to describe what is in their head. Many dreams, desires, ambitions, worries, pleasures, something sweet and soothing but actually not really sweet..
_
Wicaksono Azis
